These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, sunflower, balloon-flower
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, coral, mauve
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, librarian, architect
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, family, animation
1. the person who likes coral is the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
4. the police-officer is the person who likes mauve##1
5. the person who likes blue is in the middle##1
6. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who likes mauve##1
7. the architect is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Flower      | balloon-flower  | rose       | sunflower   |
| Color          | mauve | blue | coral |
| Job         | police-officer  | architect | librarian    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | crime       | family      |

