.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, rowing, sailing
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, red, white
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, crime, musical
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, mirinda
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
4. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes red##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Sport          | rugby      | rowing  | sailing        |
| Color         | white | red | brown |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime | musical       |
| Beverage           | mirinda     | tea     | soy-milk      |

