.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, may, march
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, rock-climbing, fishing
House: cottage, farmhouse, art-deco
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, montecristo, swisher
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is the alhambra-smoker##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the art-deco house is in the middle##1
5. the cottage house is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Birthday      | may    | october        | march |
| Hobby           | rock-climbing    | fishing | photography    |
| House   | cottage | art-deco             | farmhouse  |
| Cigar     | swisher     | alhambra                | montecristo  |

