.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, taxi, quad-bike
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, snake, dog
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, mauve, light-blue
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, aconite, tulip
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
4. the person driving the subway is the person who growstulip##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Transport          | taxi    | quad-bike  | subway      |
| Pet           | dog    | goldfish | snake |
| Color   | light-blue   | mauve  | blood-red     |
| Flower   | orchid | aconite    | tulip      |

