.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
There 3 different types of food: pepper, pear, orange
City: hamburg, paris, miami
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, mirinda
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bluemaster, blend
1. the person drinking coffee is the person traveling to paris##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
3. the person traveling to miami is the person eating orange##1
4. the person eating orange is on the far left##1
5. the pall-mall-smoker is the person eating pepper##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is the person traveling to hamburg##1
7. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food         | orange | pepper     | pear   |
| City           | miami       | paris   | hamburg     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk     | coffee | mirinda |
| Cigar           | blend      | pall-mall         | bluemaster  |

