There are 3 different nationalities: polish, australian, italian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, bolivar, havana
House: victorian, gothic-revival, craftsman
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the polish##1
2. the blend-smoker is in the middle##1
3. the italian is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the craftsman house##1
5. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Transport          | train | motorbike       | bus |
| Nationality   | italian     | polish       | australian   |
| Cigar           | bolivar      | blend       | havana     |
| House         | victorian   | gothic-revival | craftsman  |

