2. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the right of the palace house##1
4. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |     3      |
| Cigar          | oliveros       | bluemaster         | havana   |
| City           | liverpool | london | new-york |
| House   | palace     | modern        | tower        |
| Beverage   | juice      | milk           | cola        |

