.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-8::.
House: victorian, cottage, palace
3 different games are played: poker, billiard, monopoly
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, february, april
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, cricket, badminton
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the palace house is in the middle##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the victorian house##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| House         | cottage   | palace | victorian |
| Game   | poker | monopoly         | billiard       |
| Birthday           | december      | april      | february         |
| Sport     | cricket      | badminton         | rugby          |

