.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, documentary, mystery
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water, milk
There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, dutch
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, jazz, ambient
1. the fan of ambient is in the middle##1
2. the indonesian is on the far right##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is the fan of jazz##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is the dutch##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| Movie-Genre       | documentary            | martial-arts      | mystery  |
| Beverage         | milk | mirinda | water |
| Nationality         | american               | dutch | indonesian |
| Music-Genre   | jazz             | ambient       | disco      |

