There 3 different types of food: broccoli, avocado, watermelon
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, pop, blues
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, february, may
1. the person eating avocado is the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the fan of blues##1
6. the fan of pop is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Beverage           | fanta | 7up         | water |
| Food   | broccoli      | avocado | watermelon     |
| Music-Genre   | soul   | pop       | blues     |
| Birthday           | may    | february         | january        |

