The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, singing, board-games
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who growslily is on the right of the fan of punk##1
3. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who growslily##1
6. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| Flower           | orchid | lily | marigold |
| Music-Genre   | punk        | metal       | trance     |
| Sport   | snowboarding     | rugby         | baseball     |
| Hobby     | board-games | singing          | magic-tricks      |

