2. the colombian is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes red is on the right of the malaysian##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who likes green##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |      3      |
