3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is the bongani-smoker##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
6. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| City         | hamburg | liverpool | san-francisco   |
| Cigar           | prince     | ritmeester    | bongani   |
| Pet   | mouse         | hamster    | frog   |
| Movie-Genre         | documentary       | action | thriller |

