There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, lavender, aquamarine
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, zinnia, poppy
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person eating orange##1
2. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
3. the person who likes lavender is the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
5. the person who growspoppy is in the middle##1
6. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |
| Birthday         | september     | july | november |
| Food   | banana  | orange | nectarine       |
| Color   | lavender    | ivory       | aquamarine     |
| Flower     | azalea | poppy       | zinnia    |

