3. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
6. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |    3    |
| Transport      | scooter      | train    | taxi    |
| Cigar          | dannemann         | prince    | game   |
| Sport           | cycling | rugby | golf |
| Flower   | amaryllis         | zinnia     | iris    |

