City: hamburg, venice, hedgehogcher
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, blue, apricot
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, august, january
1. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person traveling to hedgehogcher is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person who likes blue is the owner of the horse##1
5. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Pet      | horse         | hedgehog     | cat     |
| City           | venice        | hedgehogcher | hamburg |
| Color   | blue        | apricot   | black    |
| Birthday         | january | june   | august |

