.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, writer, teacher
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, soy-milk
House: palace, tower, victorian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, july, november
1. the teacher is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the firefighter##1
3. the victorian house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| Job          | teacher     | writer    | firefighter    |
| Beverage         | mirinda | soy-milk | almond-milk     |
| House   | palace  | tower      | victorian        |
| Birthday         | february   | july   | november |

 